---
---
<section id="about">
  <div class="about-icons">
    <img src="/images/ico-cloud.png"  alt="" class="float-icon fi-1" />
    <img src="/images/ico-idea.png"   alt="" class="float-icon fi-2" />
    <img src="/images/ico-robot.png"  alt="" class="float-icon fi-3" />
    <img src="/images/ico-web.png"    alt="" class="float-icon fi-4" />
    <img src="/images/ico-design.png" alt="" class="float-icon fi-5" />
  </div>

  <div class="about-inner">

    <h2 class="about-title" id="aboutTitle">
      Aprende, conecta y
      <span class="blue-gradient">construye con IA</span>
    </h2>

    <p class="about-desc about-desc--1">
      <span class="bolder">AI Developer Day: Build with AI 2026</span> es el espacio
      donde la inteligencia artificial deja de ser tendencia y se convierte
      en producto. <span class="bolder">Reunimos a developers, diseñadores, estudiantes
      y profesionales tech que están construyendo soluciones reales con IA.</span>
    </p>

    <p class="about-desc about-desc--2">
      Si estás experimentando, desarrollando o liderando proyectos con IA,
      este es tu lugar para aprender, compartir y conectar con la comunidad
      que está redefiniendo el desarrollo con inteligencia artificial.
    </p>

    <p class="about-desc about-desc--3">
      <span class="bolder">Un evento pensado para inspirarte, darte herramientas prácticas
      y conectarte con la comunidad que está construyendo el presente y el
      futuro con IA.</span><br/>
      Organizado por 
        <a href="https://gdg.community.dev/gdg-callao/"
        target="_blank"
        rel="noopener">Google Developer Groups Callao.</a>
    </p>

    <a
      href="https://gdg.community.dev/e/m9699h/"
      target="_blank"
      rel="noopener"
      class="btn-primary about-cta"
      id="aboutCta"
    >
      <span>Reserva tu lugar</span>
    </a>

  </div>
</section>

<style lang="scss">
  #about {
    background: var(--blue-ultra);
    padding: 120px 80px;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;

    &::before {
      content: '';
      position: absolute;
      width: 180px;
      height: 180px;
      border: 2px solid rgba(56, 113, 205, 0.1);
      border-radius: 4px;
      top: -50px;
      right: -50px;
      transform: rotate(20deg);
    }

    &::after {
      content: '';
      position: absolute;
      width: 100px;
      height: 100px;
      border: 2px solid rgba(66, 133, 244, 0.08);
      border-radius: 4px;
      bottom: -30px;
      left: -20px;
      transform: rotate(15deg);
    }

    @media (max-width: 900px) {
      padding: 80px 28px;
    }
  }

  .about-icons {
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    pointer-events: none;
    z-index: 0;
    overflow: hidden;
  @media (max-width: 765px) {
    opacity: 0.3;
    }
  }

  .float-icon {
    position: absolute;
    animation: floatUpDown ease-in-out infinite alternate;
  }

  .fi-1 {
    width: clamp(70px, 4vw, 64px);
    top: 25%;
    left: 4%;
    animation-duration: 4s;
    animation-delay: 0s;
    rotate: 350deg;
  }

  .fi-2 {
    width: clamp(54px, 3.5vw, 56px);
    top: 5%;
    right: 50%;
    left: 50%;
    animation-duration: 5s;
    animation-delay: 0.8s;
  }

  .fi-3 {
    width: clamp(72px, 4.5vw, 70px);
    bottom: 18%;
    left: 6%;
    animation-duration: 4.5s;
    animation-delay: 1.4s;
    rotate: 11deg;
  }

  .fi-4 {
    width: clamp(69px, 3vw, 52px);
    bottom: 26%;
    right: 8%;
    animation-duration: 3.8s;
    animation-delay: 0.5s;
  }

  .fi-5 {
    width: clamp(78px, 3.8vw, 60px);
    top: 30%;
    right: 7%;
    animation-duration: 5.2s;
    animation-delay: 2s;
  }

  @keyframes floatUpDown {
    0%   { transform: translateY(0px);   }
    100% { transform: translateY(-20px); }
  }

  .about-inner {
    max-width: 720px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    text-align: center;
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
  }
  .about-title {
    font-family: var(--display);
    font-weight: 900;
    font-size: clamp(36px, 5vw, 64px);
    line-height: 1.05;
    letter-spacing: -0.04em;
    color: #0d1117;
    margin-bottom: 28px;
    opacity: 0;
  }

  @keyframes gradientFlow {
    0%   { background-position: 0%   center; }
    100% { background-position: 100% center; }
  }

  .about-desc {
    font-size: clamp(15px, 1.8vw, 18px);
    line-height: 1.75;
    color: rgba(13, 17, 23, 0.6);
    margin-bottom: 20px;
    opacity: 0;

    strong {
      color: rgba(13, 17, 23, 0.85);
      font-weight: 700;
    }

    a {
      color: var(--blue-deep);
      font-weight: 600;
      text-underline-offset: 3px;
      transition: color 0.2s;

      &:hover { color: var(--blue-mid); }
    }
  }

  .about-cta {
    margin-top: 16px;
    opacity: 0;
  }
</style>

<script>
  import { gsap } from 'gsap';
  import { ScrollTrigger } from 'gsap/ScrollTrigger';

  gsap.registerPlugin(ScrollTrigger);

  const tl = gsap.timeline({
    scrollTrigger: {
      trigger: '#about',
      start: 'top 75%',
    }
  });

  tl

    .to('#aboutTitle', {
      opacity: 1,
      y: 0,
      duration: 0.7,
      ease: 'power3.out',
    })

    .to('.about-desc', {
      opacity: 1,
      y: 0,
      duration: 0.6,
      stagger: 0.15,
      ease: 'power2.out',
    }, '-=0.3')

    .to('#aboutCta', {
      opacity: 1,
      y: 0,
      duration: 0.5,
      ease: 'power2.out',
    }, '-=0.2')

    .to('.float-icon', {
      opacity: 1,
      duration: 0.8,
      stagger: 0.1,
      ease: 'power2.out',
    }, '-=0.4');
</script>